Description: This bag is gorgeous,and has never been used! The quality, craftsmanship, and sheer beauty of the bag will take your breath away! It's a showstopper -- and it's wonderful that there are so many ways to carry it -- including as a backpack! Full description: The Red Velvet Cake Society Satchel is a delightful assembly of clever pockets, thoughtful closures and intuitive strap options to ensure smooth travel with tots. The Red Velvet Cake is crimson and cranberry vintage inspired floral European cut velvet with coordinating crimson wool tweed and crimson water resistant lining. Multiple ways to carry:As a hobo/shoulder or hand bag Cross-body (or longer on the shoulder) with the adjustable strap constructed of tweed with antique brass hardwareAs a backpack — the shoulder strap converts to the backpack by threading through internal bag loops The bag also has a "built-in changing station" zipped in around the bottom of the bag:Easy glide antique brass zipper with Cake signature zipper pullRemovable, plush changing pad And, as you'd expect from Petunia Pickle-bottom, there are pockets galore:3 organizational pockets for wipey case, diapers, and ointments4 bottle (2 outside/2 inside)5 organizational (2 outside/2 inside)Front patch pocket with magnetic snap and easy “reach and grab" cell phone pocketInternal zippered “Mommy pocket" with signature “Cake" zipper pullAntique Brass Key clip All hardware is custom stamped and sculptured with an antique brass finish Unfortunately, I can't find the stroller straps that originally came with the bag, or the red plastic Petunia Pickle Bottom wet wipes case -- although I do have a black wet wipes case I will include. Please let me know if you have any questions, and check out my other listings. Thank you for looking!
